w\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\t\twindow.google_analytics_uacct = \"UA-3380984-8\";\n</script>\n<div class=\"adsense\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\n\t\tgoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-7088061744296615\";\n\t\t/* CrawlWiki skyscraper */\n\t\tgoogle_ad_slot = \"8196155564\";\n\t\tgoogle_ad_width = 160;\n\t\tgoogle_ad_height = 600;\n-->\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n\t\t\t<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Spirit shield</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From CrawlWiki</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\">\n\t\t\t\t\tJump to:\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#mw-head\">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #33FF66; background-color: #e0fae0; border-left: 15px solid #33FF66; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Version <a href=\"/0.31\" title=\"0.31\">0.31</a></b>: This article <b>may not be</b> up to date for the <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">latest stable release</a> of Crawl.</i></div>\n<p><b>Spirit shield</b> is an intrinsic that treats your <a href=\"/MP\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"MP\">MP</a> pool as <a href=\"/HP\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"HP\">HP</a>, splitting the damage proportionally. This works on all damage sources except the <a href=\"/Poison\" title=\"Poison\">poison</a> status and HP ability costs. Should your MP reach zero, damage will be taken entirely from your HP until at least one MP is restored. HP will not be reduced to 0 before all MP is exhausted. Multiple sources of spirit shield have no extra effect.\n</p><p><a href=\"/Djinn\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Djinn\">Djinn</a> effectively have the opposite of spirit shield, using HP in place of any MP, so spirit shield has no effect.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Damage_Reduction_Example\">Damage Reduction Example</span></h3>\n<p>If you have 200 HP and 20 MP, an 11 damage attack will reduce your HP by 10 and your MP by 1. Characters with more balanced HP:MP ratios will see much more dramatic reductions to HP loss.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Sources\">Sources</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Playing as a <a href=\"/Vine_Stalker\" title=\"Vine Stalker\">Vine Stalker</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/Demonspawn_mutation\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Demonspawn mutation\">demonspawn mutation</a>, <a href=\"/Mana_Shield\" title=\"Mana Shield\">Mana Shield</a> 2</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Amulet_of_guardian_spirit\" title=\"Amulet of guardian spirit\">Amulet of guardian spirit</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Moon_troll_leather_armour\" title=\"Moon troll leather armour\">Moon troll leather armour</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Hat_of_the_Bear_Spirit\" title=\"Hat of the Bear Spirit\">Hat of the Bear Spirit</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.26\" title=\"0.26\">0.26</a>, equipping an item with the spirit shield ego would reduce your current <a href=\"/MP\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"MP\">MP</a> to 0, even if you weren't a <a href=\"/Deep_Dwarf\" title=\"Deep Dwarf\">Deep Dwarf</a>.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.25\" title=\"0.25\">0.25</a>, <a href=\"/Scarf\" title=\"Scarf\">scarves</a> could have the spirit shield ego.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.20\" title=\"0.20\">0.20</a>, <a href=\"/Hat\" title=\"Hat\">hats</a> could have the spirit shield ego. Scarves recieved it in their stead.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.10\" title=\"0.10\">0.10</a>, spirit shield would fully consume MP before you started losing health, making it less useful for casters.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916032331\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.036 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.049 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 22/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 66/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1008/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 3/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 4/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nLua time usage: 0.000s\nLua virtual size: 8.02 MB / 50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   36.711      1 -total\n100.00%   36.711      1 Template:Version031\n 96.23%   35.328      1 Template:Version\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key crawl_wiki-crawl_:pcache:idhash:6424-0!canonical and timestamp 20240916032331 and revision id 79689\n -->\n</div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Spirit_shield&amp;oldid=79689\">http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Spirit_shield&amp;oldid=79689</a>\"\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"catlinks\" class=\"catlinks\" data-mw=\"interface\"><div id=\"mw-normal-catlinks\" class=\"mw-normal-catlinks\"><a href=\"/Special:Categories\" title=\"Special:Categories\">Categories</a>: <ul><li><a href=\"/Category:0.31_articles\" title=\"Category:0.31 articles\">0.31 articles</a></li><li><a href=\"/Category:Egos\" title=\"Category:Egos\">Egos</a></li></ul></div></div>\t\t\t\t<div class=\"visualClear\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-navigation\">\n\t\t\t<h2>Navigat